1. *Razumete* li šta vam govorim? (Do you understand what I'm saying?)
2. Oni su zbunjeni pa ne *razume* sve. (They are confused, so they don't understand everything.)
3. To ne može da se *razume* na prvi pogled. (It can't be understood at first sight.)
4. *Razume* se da će morati da se strpi. (It is understood that he will have to be patient.)